name: squirt
function: Bitfield of batch fire injector events

name: iacstep
function: Stepper idle step number or PWM idle value duty

name: fuelload
function: 'Load' used for fuel table lookup e.g. equals MAP in Speed-Density

name: MAF
function: Mass Air Flow (Scaling depend on range 650g/s shown)

name: fuelload2
function: 'Load' used for fuelling on modified table

name: ignload2
function: 'Load' used for modifier ignition table lookup

name: wallfuel1
function: Calculated volume of fuel on intake walls from EAE (in injector pulsewidth units)

name: nitrous_timer_out
function: Timer used internally for nitrous system

name: n2o_addfuel
function: Fuel pulsewidth added due to nitrous system

name: n2o_retard
function: Timing retard due to nitrous system

name: water_duty
function: Duty cycle to water injection solenoid

name: fuel_pct
function: Ethanol content of fuel from Flex sensor

name: canin1
function: CAN input 1 bitfield (CAN port 1 on MS2)

name: canin2
function: CAN input 2 bitfield (CAN port 2 on MS2)

name: canout
function: CAN output 1 bitfield (CAN port 3 on MS2)
